==Month of Mizunotomi==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the Heavenly Stem is {{ill|Xin|ja|辛}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙}}), the month of {{ill|April|ja|4月}} is considered the Mizunotomi {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Old Calendar|ja|旧暦}} or on the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Risshō|ja|立夏}} to the day before {{ill|Bōshu|ja|芒種}}).

==Day of Mizunotomi==
The selection of auspicious days for Mizunotomi is as follows.
===Selected Day===
The Mizunotomi day is the 10th (final) day of {{ill|Ten Directions|ja|十方暮}} and the 1st day of {{ill|Tian Yi Tianshang|ja|天一天上}}.

