==Month of Mizunotomi==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the Heavenly Stem is {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|April|ja|4月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is considered the Mizunotomi {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or on the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (from {{ill|Risshō|ja|立夏|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Bōshu|ja|芒種|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}).

==Day of Mizunotomi==
The selection of auspicious days for Mizunotomi is as follows.
===Selected Day===
The Mizunotomi day is the 10th (final) day of {{ill|Ten Directions|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and the 1st day of {{ill|Tian Yi Tianshang|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

