In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the Heavenly Stem is {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|April|ja|4月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April|qq=}} is considered the Mizunotomi {{ill|Month (Calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Month (Calendar)|qq=}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or on the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=}} (from {{ill|Risshō|ja|立夏|1=Lixia|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Risshō|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Bōshu|ja|芒種|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bōshu|qq=}}).

